Carnage/ Dinobot

* Carnage peeked her eyes open and looked up at Teltoli, her scanners showed 
that they were only about 50 metres from the island now and she wasn't about 
to look down. She had felt the jolt and cringed, just as long as they made 
it to the island in one piece she didn't care.
Carnage looked at Cyber Claw as she flew up beside her and spoke, she 
snarled at what she told her. But what could she do about it, she was 
dangling from the front paws of a wolf with wings and couldn't do much. She 
sighed...*

" Fine, whatever. I don't care anymore."

**********************************************************

* Dinobot entered into the Ark, his rifle by his side incase somebot got the 
stupid idea to jump him. He snarled and looked at the Predacon's infront of 
him, he had made the promise to himself that he wouldn't let the bots inside 
of the ship get hurt and he planned to keep it! No matter the cost!
Suddenly he saw something that he had been waiting for ever since he had 
come back online, something that suddenly made his mech fluid boil in his 
veins!
He growled...Megatron!
His adrenalin rose and he gripped the rifle tighter, the back of his enemy 
was turned to him but he knew who it was! He knew that voice that ripped 
through his mind by spark, that poumpous and arrogant sound that had once 
told him that he was defeated mearly because he wasn't transmetal. Well, now 
things had changed!
Dinobot roared in rage at the back of his enemy...*

" MEGATRON!!!"

*Even before the echo of his voice died away Dinobot advanced towards the 
Predacon's back, he raised the rifle and began to fire. All action and 
screams were drowned out by his pure rage towards this bot, all he saw and 
heard was the Predacon in which he fired upon. Megatron!*
